  <div class="home-testimonials__item">
    <p class="body-paragraph">Deo’s presentation to the student body was well received. His description of his story in relation to how to build community was directly on point. Our international summer program has a short time to build an inclusive, welcoming, and tolerant community. Deo’s was able to show these students that they can be far from home yet keep their own identity despite the surroundings. This presentation gave the students more tools to use to gel as advisee groups, dorms, classes, and a student body. Many came up to Deo afterward to thank him, share their stories, and get advice.</p>
